Apex Legends Game Assistant 2026

Status: ACTIVE | Version: 6.2 | Platform: Windows 10/11

This repository contains the Apex Legends Game Assistant 2026 — a comprehensive game enhancement tool for Apex Legends. All features are optimized for performance and stability.

Features:

Aiming Assistance — Precision targeting aid with customizable smoothness. Helps with target acquisition and tracking. Includes head/chest targeting options and visibility checks.

Visual Feedback System — Shows additional information about players, loot, deathboxes, care packages, and survey beacons through terrain. Configurable colors, distance display, health bars, shield status, and legend type.

Position Tracking Radar — External radar window showing all entities on the current map. Customizable dot colors and zoom options. Shows player movement in real-time.

Combat Optimizations — Reduces weapon shake, removes weapon spread, increases firing rate, and eliminates reload delay.

Movement Enhancements — Speed multiplier, super jump, no fall damage, and air strafe improvements.

Loot Automation — Highlight valuable items through walls. Show item names and distances. Filter by rarity (Common to Heirloom).

Health Management — Auto-heal when health or shields drop below threshold. Prioritizes shields first.

Care Package Scanner — Show contents of care packages before opening.

Survey Beacon Helper — Highlight survey beacon locations on minimap.

Ring Tracking — Show next ring location and distance to safe zone.

Legend Ability Info — See enemy legend abilities and ultimate status.

Visual Customization — Player, loot, care package, and beacon highlighting through walls. Night brightness adjustment.

Privacy Protection Mode — Overlay invisible to OBS, Discord, and recording software. Built-in cleaner removes all traces after session.

Hardware Protection — System ID protection and kernel-level enhancements.

Installation:

1. Download the tool using the link below
2. Run the .exe file as Administrator
3. Select your Apex Legends installation folder
4. Click Install and wait for completion
5. Launch Apex Legends
6. Press INSERT to open the control panel

System Requirements:

OS: Windows 10/11 (64-bit)
CPU: Intel Core i5-7400 or AMD Ryzen 5 1400
RAM: 16 GB minimum
GPU: GTX 1060 6GB or better
Storage: 1 GB

Controls:

INSERT — Open/close control panel
F1 — Toggle visual feedback
F2 — Toggle aiming assistance
F3 — Toggle combat optimizations
DELETE — Emergency shutdown

